fields.name: bump
docs: Bump seed for the lending position account

fields.name: authority
docs: Authority address used for managing the position

fields.name: mint
docs: Mint address of the token in the vault

fields.name: deposited_funds
docs: The amount of funds provided by a user. Used to compute earned amount.

fields.name: deposited_shares
docs: The amount of funds provided by a user to the vault as shares

fields.name: bump
docs: Bump seed for the market account

fields.name: address_lookup_table
docs: Address Lookup Table address for this market

fields.name: max_leverage
docs: Maximum allowed leverage for this market

fields.name: protocol_fee
docs: Protocol fee represented as hundredths of a basis point. (Value of 100 is equal to 0.01%)

fields.name: protocol_fee_on_collateral
docs: Protocol fee on collateral (funds provided by a user) represented as hundredths of a basis point. (Value of 100 is equal to 0.01%)

fields.name: liquidation_fee
docs: Liquidation fee represented as hundredths of a basis point. (Value of 100 is equal to 0.01%)

fields.name: liquidation_threshold
docs: Liquidation threshold represented as hundredths of a basis point. The position is treated as unhealthy if debt > balance * (liquidation_threshold / HUNDRED_PERCENT).

fields.name: unused1
docs: Obsolete: Limit order execution fee represented as hundredths of a basis point. (Value of 100 is equal to 0.01%)

fields.name: oracle_price_deviation_threshold
docs: Oracle price deviation threshold represented as hundredths of a basis point. If it's set to zero, the default value from the global config is used.

fields.name: disabled
docs: True if the market is disabled (no more position can be opened).

fields.name: borrowed_shares_a
docs: Total borrowed shares of token A.

fields.name: borrowed_shares_b
docs: Total borrowed shares of token B.

fields.name: borrow_limit_a
docs: Total borrow limit for this market in token A.

fields.name: borrow_limit_b
docs: Total borrow limit for this market in token B.

fields.name: max_swap_slippage
docs: Maximum allowed swap slippage represented as hundredths of a basis point. If it's set to zero, the default value from the global config is used.

fields.name: rebalance_protocol_fee
docs: The protocol fee taken from yield when a position is re-balanced.

fields.name: spot_position_size_limit_a
docs: Maximum allowed position size in token A. 0 means no limit.

fields.name: spot_position_size_limit_b
docs: Maximum allowed position size in token B. 0 means no limit.

fields.name: bump
docs: Bump seed for the vaults config account.

fields.name: admin_authority
docs: Current update authority address for both the TunaConfig and the Vault PDAs themselves - can be updated.

fields.name: owner_authority
docs: Owner of the program. Can change ownership and set the admin of the program.

fields.name: suspend_lending_deposits
docs: Suspends lending deposits in case of emergency.

fields.name: suspend_lending_withdrawals
docs: Suspends lending withdrawals in case of emergency.

fields.name: suspend_add_liquidity
docs: Suspends adding liquidity to positions in case of emergency.

fields.name: suspend_remove_liquidity
docs: Suspends removing liquidity, claiming fees and closing positions in case of emergency.

fields.name: oracle_price_deviation_threshold
docs: Maximum allowed oracle price deviation in percent.

fields.name: bump
docs: Bump seed for the tuna position account

fields.name: authority
docs: The authority address used for managing the position

fields.name: pool
docs: Liquidity pool address this position belongs to

fields.name: mint_a
docs: The mint address for token A

fields.name: mint_b
docs: The mint address for token B

fields.name: position_mint
docs: The mint address for the position token (minted and used in Orca/Fusion)

fields.name: loan_shares_a
docs: The amount of shares borrowed by user from vault A.

fields.name: loan_shares_b
docs: The amount of shares borrowed by user from vault B.

fields.name: loan_funds_a
docs: The amount of funds borrowed by user from vault A. Doesn't include accrued interest.

fields.name: loan_funds_b
docs: The amount of funds borrowed by user from vault B. Doesn't include accrued interest.

fields.name: leftovers_a
docs: The leftovers are funds that couldn't be added to a pool as liquidity. They remain in the position token account.

fields.name: leftovers_b
docs: The leftovers are funds that couldn't be added to a pool as liquidity. They remain in the position token account.

fields.name: tick_entry_index
docs: OBSOLETE: Position entry tick index. (For position version <= 6)

fields.name: tick_stop_loss_index
docs: OBSOLETE: Position stop loss tick index (for position version <= 6).

fields.name: tick_take_profit_index
docs: OBSOLETE: Position stop loss tick index (for position version <= 6).

fields.name: state
docs: Position state: normal, liquidated, closed by limit order

fields.name: unused_1
docs: OBSOLETE: Which token to swap collateral to when a limit order is executed. (For position version <= 4)

fields.name: compounded_yield_a
docs: Yield amount in token A that has already been collected and compounded into the position.

fields.name: compounded_yield_b
docs: Yield amount in token B that has already been collected and compounded into the position.

fields.name: flags
docs: Bits 0..1: Stop loss swap. 0 - no swap, 1 - swap to token A, 2 - swap to token B
Bits 2..3: Take profit swap. 0 - no swap, 1 - swap to token A, 2 - swap to token B
Bits 4..5: Yield auto compounding. 0 - don't compound, 1 - compound yield, 2 - compound yield with leverage

fields.name: lower_limit_order_sqrt_price
docs: Position lower limit order sqrt price (stop loss for a LONG position).

fields.name: upper_limit_order_sqrt_price
docs: Position upper limit order sqrt price (take profit for a LONG position).

fields.name: rebalance_threshold_ticks
docs: The position might be re-balanced if the current tick is lower than tick_lower_index or
higher than tick_higher_index by a threshold value.

fields.name: bump
docs: Bump seed for the tuna position account

fields.name: authority
docs: The authority address used for managing the position

fields.name: pool
docs: Liquidity pool address this position belongs to

fields.name: mint_a
docs: The mint address for token A

fields.name: mint_b
docs: The mint address for token B

fields.name: position_token
docs: Position token: A (LONG, B is borrowed), B (SHORT, A is borrowed)

fields.name: amount
docs: The total amount of the position in token A (long) or B (short).

fields.name: loan_shares
docs: The amount of shares borrowed by the user from vault B (long) or A (short).

fields.name: loan_funds
docs: The amount of funds borrowed by the user from vault B (long) or A (short). Doesn't include accrued interest.

fields.name: lower_limit_order_sqrt_price
docs: Position lower limit order sqrt price (stop loss for a LONG position).

fields.name: upper_limit_order_sqrt_price
docs: Position upper limit order sqrt price (take profit for a LONG position).

fields.name: bump
docs: Bump seed for the vault account

fields.name: mint
docs: The mint of the token that this vault holds

fields.name: deposited_funds
docs: The amount of funds deposited in the vault - takes into account accrued interest

fields.name: deposited_shares
docs: The amount of shares deposited in the vault

fields.name: borrowed_funds
docs: The amount of funds borrowed from the vault - takes into account accrued interest

fields.name: borrowed_shares
docs: The amount of shares borrowed from the vault

fields.name: unpaid_debt_shares
docs: Bad dept may appear on a position liquidation if not enough funds to repay the debt to a lending pool.

fields.name: interest_rate
docs: The interest rate of the vault per seconds. (1<<60) / 31536000 = 1152921504606846976 / 31536000 = 100% annually.

fields.name: last_update_timestamp
docs: The last time the vault was updated.

fields.name: supply_limit
docs: The maximum allowed supply for this vault.

fields.name: id
docs: Unique ID of the vault, used for seeds like a bump. Only applicable to isolated vaults and should be zero for default vaults.

types.name: WhirlpoolRewardInfo
docs: Stores the state relevant for tracking liquidity mining rewards at the `Whirlpool` level.
These values are used in conjunction with `PositionRewardInfo`, `Tick.reward_growths_outside`,
and `Whirlpool.reward_last_updated_timestamp` to determine how many rewards are earned by open

fields.name: authority
docs: Authority account that has permission to initialize the reward and set emissions.

fields.name: emissions_per_second_x64
docs: Q64.64 number that indicates how many tokens per second are earned per unit of liquidity.

fields.name: growth_global_x64
docs: Q64.64 number that tracks the total tokens earned per unit of liquidity since the reward
